n: Easy Spicy Ketchup Dip for Sweet Potato Fries
des: "A ketchup-based dip that is sweet and spicy with plenty of zing that is best served with sweet potato French fries. The longer you let this sit, the better. My friends and family can't get enough of this stuff!"
ins: Mix ketchup, Worcestershire sauce, horseradish, brown sugar, cayenne pepper, and garlic salt together in a bowl.
